SELECT
  $__timeGroup(Datetime,$__interval) as 'time',
  sum(ENCOUNTER)/count(ENCOUNTER) as 'area: avg_encounters',
  sum(GET_MAP_OBJECTS)/count(GET_MAP_OBJECTS) as 'area: avg_get_map_objects',
  sum(REMOVE_QUEST)/count(REMOVE_QUEST) as 'area: avg_remove_quest',
  sum(ENCOUNTER) as 'area: encounters',
  sum(GET_MAP_OBJECTS) as 'area: get_map_objects',
  sum(REMOVE_QUEST) as 'area: remove_quest',
  count(GET_PLAYER) as 'area: #disconnects',
  sum(DISK_ENCOUNTER) as 'area: lure encounters',
  sum(GET_HOLOHOLO_INVENTORY) as 'area: get_holoholo_inventory',
  sum(GET_PLAYER) as 'area: get_player',
  sum(FORT_DETAILS) as 'area: fort_details',
  sum(GYM_GET_INFO) as 'area: get_gym_info',
  sum(RECYCLE_INVENTORY_ITEM) as 'area: recycle_inventory_item',
  sum(FORT_SEARCH) as 'area: fort_search',
  sum(GET_RAID_LOBBY_COUNTER) as 'area: get_raid_lobby_counter',
  sum(duration/3600)/count(duration) as 'area: avg_accountUse'

FROM stats_account
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(datetime) AND
  worker not regexp '${fortWorker}' AND
  substring_index(worker,'_',1) in ($Area) AND
  worker in ($Worker) AND
  account in ($Account)
GROUP BY 1
ORDER BY $__timeGroup(Datetime,$__interval)
